videos.description: Rutgers forces a turnover and get out in transition with Ron Harper Jr. scoring the layup plus the foul and calling for noise from the crowd.
videos.headline: Harper pumped after Rutgers and-1

videos.description: Andre Wesson finds his brother, Kaleb, down low and the big man finishes with the one-handed jam.
